# =============================================================================
# File: /opt/ansible-k3s-cluster/README.cluster-integrity-model
# =============================================================================
# Purpose:
#   Define the integrity model for the cluster. This ensures that all files,
#   artifacts, and configurations remain consistent, verifiable, and trusted.
#
# Integrity Components:
#
#   1. File Integrity
#      - wc-based manifest
#      - ASCII-safe documentation
#
#   2. Artifact Integrity
#      - Verified kernel artifacts
#      - Verified module dependencies
#
#   3. Configuration Integrity
#      - Kernel config drift detection
#      - Bootloader config drift detection
#
#   4. Operational Integrity
#      - Preflight checks
#      - Postchecks
#      - Rollback strategy
#
# Notes:
#   - This file defines the authoritative integrity model for the cluster.
# =============================================================================
